[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.0,
    "text": "How sentimental."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "You know, I haven't been this choked up since I got a hunk of moussaka caught in my throat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "So, is this an audience or a mosaic?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "Hey, how you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Looking good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "Nice dress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "So, Hades, you finally made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "How are things in the underworld?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "Well, they're just fine, you know, a little dark, a little gloomy, and as always, hey, full of dead people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "What are you going to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "Join the celebration."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Hey, love to, babe, but unlike you gods lounging about up here, I regrettably have a full-time gig that you, by the way, so charitably bestowed on me, Zeus, so can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Love to, but can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "Kill myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "If only, if only."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "As mean as he was ruthless, and that's the gospel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "The fates are here and you didn't tell me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "Anyway, see, ladies, I was at this party and I lost track of time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "We know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "You know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "So, here's the deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Zeus, Mr. High and Mighty, Mr. Hey, you, get off of my clout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "Now he has a bouncing baby butt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "We know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "You know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "I got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "I got the concept."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Unleash the titans, you monstrous band."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm, good, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "And you, Hades, will rule all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Yes, Sir Hades, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "A word of caution to this tale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 93.0,
    "text": "Excuse me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Okay, fine, fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "I'm cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "I'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "Meg."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Speak of the devil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Meg, my little flower, my little bird, my little nut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "I thought you were gonna persuade the river guardian to join my team for the uprising, and here I am, kind of river guardian-less."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "It wasn't my fault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "It was this wonder boy, Hercules."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "What was that name again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Hercules."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "He comes on with his big innocent farm boy routine, but I could see through that in a Peloponnesian minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "I'm about to rearrange the cosmos, and the one schmiel who can last it up is waltzing around in the woods!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Fortunately for the three of you, we still have time to correct this rather egregious oversight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "And this time, no foul-ups."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Stirring performance, boys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "I was really moved."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "And hey, two thumbs way, way up for our leading lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "What a dish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "What a doll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Guys, guys, relax."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "It's only halftime, game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Set."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Match."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Pull!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "Nice shooting, Rex."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "I can't believe this guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "I throw everything I've got at him, and it doesn't even..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "What are those?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "I've got 24 hours to get rid of this bozo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Meg, my sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "Don't even go there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "See, he's got to have a weakness, because everybody's got a weakness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "I mean, for what, Pandora?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "It was the box thing for the Trojans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "Hey, they bet on the wrong horse, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "You give me the key to bringing down Wonder Breath."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry, you mind running that by me again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "I must have a chunk of brimstone wedged in my ear or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Then read my lips."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Forget it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "Meg, Meg, Meg, my sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "Minion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Aren't we forgetting one teensy-weensy bit ever so crucial?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 238.0,
    "text": "The tiny detail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.0,
    "endTime": 238.0,
    "text": "I own you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.0,
    "endTime": 241.0,
    "text": "Hear that sound?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "It's the sound of your freedom, cluttering out the window forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "I can't believe you're getting so worked up about some guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 251.0,
    "text": "This one is different."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "He's honest, and he's sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "Please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "He would never do anything to hurt me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "He's a guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "Ba-boom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "Name is Hades, Lord of the Dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Hi, how you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Not now, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.0,
    "endTime": 264.0,
    "text": "Hey, hey, I only need a few seconds, and I'm a fast talker, all right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 266.0,
    "text": "See, I've got this major deal in the works, a real estate venture, if you will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 269.0,
    "text": "And, Herc, you little devil, may I call you Herc?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 271.0,
    "text": "You seem to be constantly getting in the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.0,
    "endTime": 272.0,
    "text": "You've got the wrong guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.0,
    "endTime": 273.0,
    "text": "Give me your little..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.0,
    "endTime": 277.0,
    "text": "Dance, we kiss, we schmooze, we carry on, we go home happy, what do you say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 279.0,
    "text": "Nah, I mean, it's a possibility."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "It happens, you know, it's war, but what can I tell you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Anyway, what are you all these people, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Isn't Meg..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 286.0,
    "text": "Isn't she more important than David?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.0,
    "endTime": 287.0,
    "text": "Stop it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.0,
    "endTime": 288.0,
    "text": "Isn't she?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.0,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "What do you say we shake him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.0,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": "I really don't have, like, time to bat this around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.0,
    "endTime": 294.0,
    "text": "I'm kind of on a schedule here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.0,
    "endTime": 295.0,
    "text": "I've got plans for August, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.0,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "I need an answer, like, now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "Damn!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "Uh, guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "Olympus would be that way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.0,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "Dude!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 305.0,
    "text": "And I think I'm gonna like it here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.0,
    "endTime": 310.0,
    "text": "Guys, get your titanic rears in gear and kick some Olympian butt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.0,
    "endTime": 312.0,
    "text": "Whoa, is my hair out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.0,
    "endTime": 316.0,
    "text": "Because our little Nat Meg has to go all noble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.0,
    "endTime": 322.0,
    "text": "You see, Meg's running with a new crowd these days and not a very lively one at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.0,
    "endTime": 327.0,
    "text": "The son of my hated rival trapped forever in a river of death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.0,
    "endTime": 328.0,
    "text": "Going once!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.0,
    "endTime": 330.0,
    "text": "Is there a downside to this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.0,
    "endTime": 330.0,
    "text": "Going twice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.0,
    "endTime": 332.0,
    "text": "Okay, okay, okay, okay, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.0,
    "endTime": 333.0,
    "text": "You get her out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.0,
    "endTime": 334.0,
    "text": "She goes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.0,
    "endTime": 335.0,
    "text": "You stay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.0,
    "endTime": 337.0,
    "text": "You know what's on my mind?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.0,
    "endTime": 339.0,
    "text": "You'll be dead before you can get to her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.0,
    "endTime": 340.0,
    "text": "Hercules, stop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.0,
    "endTime": 345.0,
    "text": "You can't do this to me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.0,
    "endTime": 345.0,
    "text": "You can't!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.0,
    "endTime": 346.0,
    "text": " Okay, well, I deserve that."
  }
]